  "notes": "Marty_Party - Personal Assistant Telegram Bot Workflow\n\nFlow:\n1. Telegram Trigger receives messages from Marty_Party_Bot\n2. Skill lookup checks bot.skills table for matching commands\n3. If skill matched → routes to direct handler (daily_tasks, add_task, complete_task, morning_briefing, network_status)\n4. If no skill → Claude API with conversation history for intelligent responses\n5. Claude can detect actions (create/update tasks) and execute them\n6. All conversations saved to personal.conversations for context\n\nCredentials needed:\n- Telegram Bot API (Marty Party Bot)\n- PostgreSQL (AuditOS - 100.68.214.22:5432)\n- Anthropic API Key (for Claude claude-sonnet-4-6)\n\nError handling: Any failure sends a friendly error message to the user."
